The paper deals with the problem of secure communication in a network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of codes to achieve secure communication, which falls under the category of coding theory (cs.CR). The problem of disseminating messages from multiple sources to multiple destinations is a network problem, which can be categorized under distributed systems (cs.DS) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
